### Test AG-UI Server Endpoints
### Use VS Code REST Client extension or similar tools

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5100

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### Simple Query - No Thread ID
POST {{baseUrl}}/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "messages": [
    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "What is the capital of France?"
    }
  ],
  "context": {}
}

### Query with Thread ID (for conversation continuity)
POST {{baseUrl}}/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "threadId": "thread_abc123",
  "messages": [
    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Tell me more about Paris"
    }
  ],
  "context": {}
}

### Complex Query
POST {{baseUrl}}/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "threadId": "thread_complex_001",
  "runId": "run_001",
  "messages": [
    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Explain quantum computing in simple terms, then give me 3 real-world applications"
    }
  ],
  "context": {
    "user_level": "beginner",
    "language": "en"
  }
}

### List Active Threads
GET {{baseUrl}}/threads

### Delete Thread
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/threads/thread_abc123

